                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable H</hi> 138.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner Rourke's former conviction from Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read)—I</hi> was present at the trial—he is the person described.</p>
               <p>(Miles Costello, of No. 5, Green-bank, Tooley-street, and Mrs.——, gave Rourke a good character.)</p>
